; Coverage test for post.cc lines 309-310, 157-158, 550-558
; Tests display_account and xact_id accessors.
; display_account returns the account name as it should be displayed.
; xact_id returns the 1-based index of the posting within its transaction.

2024/03/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Expenses:Drink     $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(display_account) %(xact_id)\n"
Expenses:Food 1
Expenses:Drink 2
Assets:Cash 3
end test
